  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "FcfsuPGRQP3nNBcVHa0hbMFffyw=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "The Operational Hub service offering has four tiers:\n\n**Essentials (free)**\nSelf-service tools: legal document templates, global invoice generator, budget generator, needs analysis. Also includes exchange setup, crypto-friendly banking, off-ramp setup, EOR/PEO setup, payment controls, and audit support. Plus AI agent services (information retrieval, document generation, data entry, workflow execution, task routing, reporting). This tier is the top of the funnel \u2014 free tools that demonstrate value.\n\n**Starter**\nEverything in Essentials plus: Swiss Association setup with licensed counsel, registered address in Zug, VAT registration, annual tax filing, reimbursement management, invoice management, monthly accounting & close, monthly expense reports.\n\n**Standard**\nEverything in Starter plus: expense policies, contributor onboarding & operations, multi-currency payouts (crypto-to-fiat in USD/GBP/EUR/CHF/DKK within 48h), dedicated ops support. Also adds compliance services: supplier & partner liaison, AML monitoring, contractor documentation, invoice compliance review, card & spend operations, legal counsel advice (5 hours).\n\n**Custom**\nEverything in Standard plus: multiple entities, dedicated account manager, admin portal, custom workflows & reporting.\n\nBilling cycles: quarterly or annual. The tiered structure creates a natural upsell path from free tools to full-service operations.",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z"
    }
  },
